            k
          
          
            2
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sigma _{k}^{2}}
   be the Bessel corrected variance of the values in 
  
    
      
        x
      
    
    {\displaystyle x}
   associated with class 
  
    
      
        
          C
          
            k
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle C_{k}}
  . Suppose one has collected some observation value 
  
    
      
        v
      
    
    {\displaystyle v}
  . Then, the probability density of 
  
    
      
        v
      
    
    {\displaystyle v}
   given a class 
  
    
      
        
          C
          
            k
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle C_{k}}
  , i.e., 
  
    
      
        p
        (
