    {\displaystyle \sigma _{k}^{2}}
  . Formally,

  
    
      
        p
        (
        x
        =
        v
        ∣
        
          C
          
            k
          
        
        )
        =
        
          
            1
            
              2
              π
              
                σ
                
                  k
                
                
                  2
                
              
            
          
        
        
        
