    {\displaystyle p({\text{foot size}}\mid {\text{male}})={\frac {1}{\sqrt {2\pi \sigma ^{2}}}}\exp \left({\frac {-(8-\mu )^{2}}{2\sigma ^{2}}}\right)=1.3112\cdot 10^{-3}}
  

  
    
      
        
